OL,7,FA 27-year-old man who "befriended and
OL,8,Fabducted two children" before sexually
OL,9,Fassaulting them at a Lincolnshire
OL,10,Fseaside resort has been jailed.
OL,12,FJason Hoodlass who was described in
OL,13,Fcourt as "an exceptionally high risk
OL,14,Fto the public" lured the two girls to
OL,15,Fa tourist attraction in to abuse them
OL,16,Fand take indecent images.
OL,18,FHoodlass also took the children to a
OL,19,Fshop in Grimsby town centre where he
OL,20,Ffilmed them in the changing rooms.
