OL,7,FJeremy Evans, prosecuting, said the
OL,8,Fgirls had visited the seafront at
OL,9,FCleethorpes and were in an arcade when
OL,10,FHoodlass spotted them and started
OL,11,Fwatching them.
OL,13,FStreet cameras captured him making
OL,14,Fcontact with the girls. He took them
OL,15,Fto Ross Castle where he sexually
OL,16,Fassaulted them and took pictures on
OL,17,Fhis phone.
