OL,5,Cpredator
OL,7,FHoodlass then accompanied them to
OL,8,FGrimsby town centre where he filmed
OL,9,Fthem trying clothes on in a fitting
OL,10,Froom shop. Mr Evans said Hoodlass
OL,11,Fspend #30 on children's clothes,
OL,12,Fjewellery and drinks for the girls.
OL,14,FAfter a couple of hours the girls left
OL,15,Fhis company, saying they were going to
OL,16,Fmeet someone and raised the alarm.
OL,18,FHoodlass of Immingham, admitted two
OL,19,Foffences of abduction and an offence
OL,20,Fof voyeurism.
