OL,7,FJudge Richard Woolfall told Hoodlass:
OL,8,F"You have a sexual preoccupation with
OL,9,Fchildren."
OL,11,FHe said the children had gone to the
OL,12,Fbeach to play when Hoodlass noticed
OL,13,Fthey were not in the company of an
OL,14,Fadult.
OL,16,FHe added: "For three-and-a-half hours
OL,17,Fyou had those children in your
OL,18,Fcontrol. You did that because you
OL,19,Fwanted to sexually abuse those
OL,20,Fchildren.
