OL,7,F"Ross Castle was designed to provide a
OL,8,Fvantage point. It gave you the perfect
OL,9,Fplace to carry out your offences. It
OL,10,Fgave you a good view of anyone that
OL,11,Fwas coming. You groomed, befriended
OL,12,Fand abducted these two children."
OL,14,FJudge Woolfall described the events as
OL,15,F"every parent's worst nightmare".
OL,17,FHe added: "They are living with this.
OL,18,FYou did not give that a second
OL,19,Fthought. You were driven by your own
OL,20,Fselfish sexual desires."
